title: Me, a lvl 18 full build kayle split pushing and drawing all the enemies to me.
body:
my team, doesn't push lanes, take towers or try for objectives when there is literally 4 of the enemies bot trying to kill me. 
our tank support had the score of 0/6/6 out of 36 team kills. 
our diana jg is 5/14/7

it doesn't matter who the hell you play, or what you do, unless you're a smurf...you literally cannot carry stupidity
